data.description: This may be your opportunity to buy into highly sought after Hobcaw Point. This sweet little one story is in need of updating.  It has oak floors throughout the main living rooms, halls and bedrooms.  Spacious living room. Separate dining room opens to back yard. Kitchen has a roomy walk-in pantry.  Enclosed breezeway to garage makes a great home office.  This home has two spacious bedrooms and full bath with tub/shower off hallway past the living room.  Paneled den can be third bedroom.  Half bath is located off front hall adjacent to den.  Hobcaw Yacht Club membership available to residents with board approval and little wait time. Enjoy the amenities and family events HYC offers. Enjoy this great location, close to schools, shopping & downtown! Property being sold strictly ''As is.''
